text: karpit trong ban hamkhat champoh puok anak nouv satv slab ning chheam ning sach chrouk haeyning ei v delke saamleh daembi baucha mcheasa phe sa ng krawpi a l laoh . hetonih bokkol na trauv ban ke bangkham(aoy ttuoltean avei teangnih) daoy poum mean chetnea ning min leusa pi tamrouv karchabach noh pit bra dk nasa a l laoh mha aphytosa mha anet sraleanh
